OL,3,CRightmove gives reasons why June saw
OL,4,Can 'unusual' asking price fall
OL,6,FThe average price tag on a home fell
OL,7,Fby 0.6% or #2,113 in June, in the
OL,8,Fbiggest price drop recorded for this
OL,9,Fmonth of the year in 14 years,
OL,10,Faccording to a property website.
OL,12,FThe month-on-month fall took the
OL,13,Faverage asking price across Britain to
OL,14,F#376,191, Rightmove said.
OL,16,FThe month of June typically sees
OL,17,Fmodest price increases, Rightmove said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
