OL,3,CRightmove gives reasons why June saw
OL,4,Can 'unusual' asking price fall
OL,6,FIt added that May's warmer weather may
OL,7,Fhave kick-started the usual summer
OL,8,Fslowdown earlier than usual this year,
OL,9,Fwhile the World Cup may also prove to
OL,10,Fbe a distraction for some home movers.
OL,12,FRightmove also said that more
OL,13,Faffordable parts of Britain, such as
OL,14,Fthe North East of England and
OL,15,FScotland, are seeing prices hold up
OL,16,Frelatively well, compared with this
OL,17,Ftime last year.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1781484490
OL,3,CRightmove gives reasons why June saw
OL,4,Can 'unusual' asking price fall
OL,6,FColleen Babcock, property expert at
OL,7,FRightmove, said: "It's unusual to see
OL,8,Fa price fall of this size in June, as
OL,9,Fwe would normally expect to see modest
OL,10,Fprice growth at this point in the year.
OL,12,F"What's different this time is a
OL,13,Fcombination of factors, including
OL,14,Fwider economic uncertainty, the timing
OL,15,Fof the May bank holiday and unusual
OL,16,Fheatwave, and the high number of homes
OL,17,Fon the market, which together appear
OL,18,Fto be bringing forward the
OL,19,Ftraditionally slower summer market.
OL,26,@oD@ROUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1781484490
OL,3,CRightmove gives reasons why June saw
OL,4,Can 'unusual' asking price fall
OL,6,F"In this kind of market, sellers need
OL,7,Fto work harder to attract attention.
OL,9,F"Setting a competitive asking price
OL,10,Ffrom the outset is key, as buyers are
OL,11,Ftaking more time to compare options
OL,12,Fand are quick to move on if a home
OL,13,Fdoesn't stand out on value."
OL,15,FRightmove said higher mortgage rates
OL,16,Fare continuing to weigh on activity as
OL,17,Fmany household budgets are squeezed,
OL,18,Fwhile the wider choice of homes for
OL,19,Fsale is encouraging buyers to take a
OL,20,Fless urgent approach unless a property
OL,21,Freally stands out.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@AOUuD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1781484490
OL,3,CRightmove gives reasons why June saw
OL,4,Can 'unusual' asking price fall
OL,6,FMs Babcock added: "While the summer
OL,7,Fmarket has come a bit early this year,
OL,8,Foverall activity is still within a
OL,9,Ftypical historic range.
OL,11,F"What has changed is some buyer
OL,12,Fbehaviour; with more homes to choose
OL,13,Ffrom and higher borrowing costs,
OL,14,Fbuyers are deliberating more and
OL,15,Ftaking longer over their decisions."
OL,26,@nD@SOUsD@AOUwD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
