OL,3,CRightmove gives reasons why June saw
OL,4,Can 'unusual' asking price fall
OL,6,FMatt Smith, a mortgage expert at
OL,7,FRightmove, said: "It's encouraging to
OL,8,Fsee mortgage rates edging down
OL,9,Fslightly, and even relatively small
OL,10,Freductions can make a difference to
OL,11,Fbuyers' budgets."
OL,13,FMarc von Grundherr, director of Benham
OL,14,Fand Reeves, London, said: "Buyers
OL,15,Faren't moving at the pace we've seen
OL,16,Fin previous years, largely because
OL,17,Fcurrent market conditions and an
OL,18,Foversupply of stock are affording them
OL,19,Fthe luxury of both time and choice."
OL,26,@oD@ROUsD@QO]vD@[OU{D@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
