OL,3,CRightmove gives reasons why June saw
OL,4,Can 'unusual' asking price fall
OL,6,FHenry Crane, a partner at James
OL,7,FLaurence Estate Agents, Birmingham,
OL,8,Fsaid: "Overall, while demand remains,
OL,9,Fit is highly price-sensitive and
OL,10,Fselective, with the best-positioned
OL,11,Fhomes continuing to perform strongly."
OL,13,FMatthew Harvey, a partner at Tayler &
OL,14,FFletcher, Cotswolds, said: "Demand in
OL,15,Fthe higher middle market remains
OL,16,Fsteady, led by lifestyle and schooling
OL,17,Fneeds.
OL,26,@pD@GOUsD@fO]vD@\OU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
