OL,3,CRightmove gives reasons why June saw
OL,4,Can 'unusual' asking price fall
OL,6,F"At the top end, price adjustments are
OL,7,Flargely a correction of earlier
OL,8,Foverpricing following the post-Covid
OL,9,Fsurge.
OL,11,F"Overall, realistically-priced homes
OL,12,Fare selling well, with many recent
OL,13,Flistings already finding buyers."
OL,15,FThe report was released as a separate
OL,16,Findex from property firm Hamptons
OL,17,Findicated that the average price of a
OL,18,Fnewly agreed let in Britain rose 1.1%
OL,19,Fover the year to May, slowing from a
OL,20,F1.2% annual increase in April.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUuD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
