OL,3,CRightmove gives reasons why June saw
OL,4,Can 'unusual' asking price fall
OL,6,FThe average rent paid by a tenant
OL,7,Fmoving into a property in Britain was
OL,8,F#1,382 per month in May, Hamptons said.
OL,10,FRegionally, the average new let rent
OL,11,Fin the South East of England reached
OL,12,F#1,500 per month in May, up by 2.0%
OL,13,Fannually.
OL,15,FHamptons said this is the first time
OL,16,Fit has recorded any region outside
OL,17,FLondon with rents reaching the #1,500-
OL,18,Fper-month mark.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1781484490
OL,3,CRightmove gives reasons why June saw
OL,4,Can 'unusual' asking price fall
OL,6,FAneisha Beveridge, head of research at
OL,7,FHamptons, said: "While rental growth
OL,8,Fon newly agreed lets remains cool by
OL,9,Frecent standards, landlords appear to
OL,10,Fbe taking a more cautious approach
OL,11,Fwhen selecting new tenants.
OL,13,F"Many are showing a willingness to
OL,14,Fwait for the right tenant rather than
OL,15,Faccept the first offer, which has
OL,16,Freduced the number of homes let and
OL,17,Fhelped to keep a lid on rental growth
OL,18,Ffor new tenants."
OL,26,@oD@QOUuD@AOUzD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
