OL,3,CRightmove gives reasons why June saw
OL,4,Can 'unusual' asking price fall
OL,6,FHamptons' monthly lettings index has
OL,7,Fbeen running since 2011 and uses data
OL,8,Ffrom the Connells Group to track
OL,9,Fchanges to the cost of renting. The
OL,10,Findex is based on achieved rather than
OL,11,Fadvertised rents.
OL,13,FHere are average monthly rents for
OL,14,Fnewly let homes in May, according to
OL,15,FHamptons, and the annual change:
OL,17,FLondon, #2,294, 0.6%
OL,19,FEast of England, #1,225, 0.3%
OL,21,FSouth East, #1,500, 2.0%
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
